{"tid":1995471,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一不小心犯聚了 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-04-30T09:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T09:27:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"61ecb06f681a38a2f6da79feba7fd4d177f3aa96","tid":1995471,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:27:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200430/20909417/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200430%2F20909417%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=f91c5f1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200430%2F20909417%2F&h=9fc3a913\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200430/20909417/</a><br />\n<br />\n一不小心犯聚了 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200430/large/1588145951_e79d.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200430%2Flarge%2F1588145951_e79d.jpg&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=f9d0bb0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200430/large/1588145951_e79d.jpg</a><br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n看照片，警方今日凌晨高調逮捕兩極具社會地位之名人：毛主席和金元帥，和一群美女。<br />\n<br />\n繼周日傍晚，太古城商場中庭及各層欄杆位置逾千人舉行「和你唱」活動，《願榮光歸香港》歌聲、「五大訴求缺一不可」口號，。。。<br />\n<br />\n，令黑警之O T大幅減少，因此不得不多利用「限聚令」搵食。<br />\n<br />\n根據警方釋法：「任何出席公眾活動人士，如抱有共同聚集目的，群組活動有多於。。。。限聚令。」此外，「群組聚集者相距不足1.5米，均屬違法。」<br />\n<br />\n這599G章禁令，並非雞毛當令箭，考試、購物、行山、拜祭、排。。。的，即時墮入法網。若指濫捕自己同法官講。<br />\n<br />\n即使被捕的毛主席和金元帥，只被美女。。。我哋唔會理會背景，如果你唔想畀我拉，唔該你唔好犯法！」 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}